{
  "id": "adv_event_2306_02_04_01",
  "title": "STAGE4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、さとみさん\n今日は来てくれてありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for coming today‚\n{user}-san and Satomi-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.6541725159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、突然呼び出されたらびっくりしますよね\n次は私達サニーピースの番です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ it's surprising to be called out suddenly‚ right?\nNext up is our turn‚ Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8666666667,
      "endTime": 14.750000158999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "……うーん、なんだか毎日会ってるのに\nこうして感謝を伝えるのって緊張するなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm‚ even though we see each other every day‚\nI still get nervous expressing gratitude like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9666666667,
      "endTime": 23.2962362926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん……尺が、ある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan… we have a time limit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5,
      "endTime": 26.3399999619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "わわっ、そうだよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5333333333,
      "endTime": 28.754943331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……二人がいつもヘトヘトになるまで\n星見プロのために働いてくれているのを知っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… I know that you two always work hard\nfor Hoshimi Prods‚ until you get tired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9666666667,
      "endTime": 36.8240363758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "でも、みんなの前ではそんな素振りさえ見せない\n二人には感謝しかありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you never show signs of it in front of everyone‚ and\nWe can't thank you enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0333333333,
      "endTime": 45.062856992099995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "私達は、そんな二人が大好きだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We really love you two.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2666666667,
      "endTime": 48.668344561299996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私達……BIG4になれました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ we… became part of the BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.8666666667,
      "endTime": 53.4162813823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "なんだかしばらくバタバタしてたけど……\nこの機会に、五人で集まって思い返してみたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Things have been chaotic lately…\nSo‚ we took this chance to gather and reminisce.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.6,
      "endTime": 61.7256011009,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら、やっぱり二人が、支えてくれていたからだね\nって意見で一致",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And we all agreed that\nit was because of you two",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9333333333,
      "endTime": 68.6933333714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "きっと{user}さんは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Surely‚ {user}-san… You'll say‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9,
      "endTime": 71.2461905003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "「みんなが頑張ったからだ、俺は何も……」\nって言いますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"It's because everyone else worked hard‚ not me…\"\nRight?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4333333333,
      "endTime": 77.5402948697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "でもそんなことないの、絶対\n私達だけじゃここまで来ることは出来なかったよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that's not true‚ definitely not\nWe couldn't have come this far without you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.7333333333,
      "endTime": 85.155736955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "二人がいなかったら、{user}さんと\nさとみさんがいなかったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Without you two‚ {user}-san\nand Satomi-san‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3666666667,
      "endTime": 90.95873037979999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに輝くことは出来ませんでした！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "we wouldn't be shining like this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1666666667,
      "endTime": 93.76897951769999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "だから今日は、私達サニーピースが\n二人のためだけに歌います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why today‚ Sunny Peace\nwill sing just for you two!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9666666667,
      "endTime": 99.7351925532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_04-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "今までの感謝を、ぜーんぶ込めて歌います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll put all our gratitude into this song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9333333333,
      "endTime": 104.0503854592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
